metadata.name: LiquiDoodle #1
metadata.desc: LiquiDoodles are a collection of 10,000 NFTs (non-fungible tokens) that are made up of hundreds of exciting visual traits designed by Artificial Intelligence . Inspired by the Doodles; LiquiDoodles include skellys, cats, aliens, apes and mascots. The LiquiDoodles collection also includes dozens of rare heads, costumes, and colorways of the artist's palette mixed with Artificial Intelligence.
